com.oym.indoor.location

Class IndoorLocationLib

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oym.indoor.location.IndoorLocationLib

  • public class IndoorLocationLib
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the entering point of the Indoor Location SDK. It will takes care of starting the indoor service, compute the position and notify the user the position and triggered notification.
